{
  "stem": "895.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, always, they threw their luggage where we were nearly working, near the [INAUDIBLE], in the corner.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, if they're not looking, go over to the luggage and see.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's what-- we look-- we saw all what we saw, celery, walnuts, and everything in the food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we hided it, before they could see us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we went out of my shift, then he got a pail, and we made soup behind the barracks that the Germans didn't see.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, one day I was caught by one of the Nazis with a piece of bread I took from the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My whole face was blue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I see that one soldier, who gave me the chance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He goes, what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hitting me, because I stole a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I still worked as a barber.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then they put me in the sauna, where I had to put on the showers, with the woman naked.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember one woman, she survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She lives in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Had a gold chain which she was hiding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, can you get me something for that?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, I'll try.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the people came in from-- with barrels with potatoes and that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were trying to get things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I gave them the chain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They gave me a big piece of sausage-- blood sausage, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I gave her that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the stuff what we got in the-- in the-- in the clothes, from the people-- we sometimes tore it open when they weren't looking.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Diamonds and everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we hided them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My friend-- in the war, we couldn't find him anymore, after the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had so much gold and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
